      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car remains a reliable daily driver, you will notice some cosmetic imperfections including minor dings on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, but it is not a showroom piece; it's a practical choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point.",
