    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been so reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver. It's been well-loved and is ready to hit the road for its next adventure. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-focused example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock for precise torque vectoring. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe carrier and overhauled VANOS seals. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry but benefits from refreshed bushings to maintain sharp turn-in and lateral stability. The engine exhibits a healthy power band with consistent compression across all six cylinders. A transparently maintained icon optimized for mechanical longevity and analog performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs reliably.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a reliable, well-cared-for car that performs beautifully as a daily driver. The exterior paint maintains a high-gloss luster, though a few minor surface scratches and typical stone chips on the hood are present upon close inspection. All body panels are straight with consistent gaps. Inside, you'll find a clean, non-smoking interior where the upholstery remains firm and free of tears, showing only light entry-wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system and steering wheel controls, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no odd noises or leaks, backed by a consistent maintenance record. The transmission shifts crisply through all gears. The tires are matching set with plenty of tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently serviced. This is a solid, honest car that has been maintained to a high standard and is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
